T01TD1136E:83a-1: ban da na sto tra n'a ma /
T01TD1136E:83a-3: phyag 'tshal ba'i bstod pa zhes bya ba //
T01TD1136E:83a-4: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad la phyag 'tshal lo//
T01TD1136E:83a-5: gnod byed 'dod chags zhe sdang dang //
T01TD1136E:83a-6: srid 'khor rmongs chen dra ba spangs //
T01TD1136E:83a-7: mchog sbyin mdzad pa rgyal ba mchog / mchog byung sangs rgyas bdag phyag 'tshal //
T01TD1136E:83a-8: yang dag thugs chud rdzogs sangs rgyas //
T01TD1136E:83a-9: lha dang lha min mchod byas pa //
T01TD1136E:83a-10: 'jig rten gsum gyi bla ma la //
T01TD1136E:83b-0: mi @83b pham mnyam pa med gyur cing //
T01TD1136E:83b-1: bdud stobs pham mdzad bdag phyag 'tshal //
T01TD1136E:83b-3: gdud ni nyi ma'i rigs su grags //
T01TD1136E:83b-4: dpa' bo rmad byung sangs rgyas ni //
T01TD1136E:83b-5: yon tan tshogs ni bsdus pa la //
T01TD1136E:83b-6: lha mi rlung lhas mchod phyag 'tshal //
T01TD1136E:83b-7: gser gyi ri bo'i rtse 'dra'i sku //
T01TD1136E:83b-9: gser gyi mdog dang ldan gyur cing //
T01TD1136E:83b-10: sum cu rtsa gnyis mtshan dang ldan //
T01TD1136E:83b-11: shis ldan mtshan bzang phyag 'tshal lo //
T01TD1136E:83b-12: me dang glog dang me stag dang //
T01TD1136E:83b-13: nyi zer stong ldan dkyil 'khor can //
T01TD1136E:83b-14: gang gis stobs ni brgyan gyur pa //
T01TD1136E:83b-15: mnyam med stobs ldan phyag 'tshal lo //
T01TD1136E:83b-16: dpal ldan mchog ni 'bar ba yi //
T01TD1136E:83b-17: bsod dang dul bar yang dag ldan //
T01TD1136E:83b-18: thub pa'i dbang po mchog gyur ba //
T01TD1136E:83b-19: yang dag byang chub brnyes pa la //
T01TD1136E:83b-20: ches dregs phyag byas phyag 'tshal lo //
T01TD1136E:83b-21: gang zhig sems can phan mdzad cing //
T01TD1136E:83b-22: bde ba'i don phyir snying rjes 'jug / yang dag don la zhugs gyur pas //
T01TD1136E:83b-25: lha dang lha min phyag byas pa //
T01TD1136E:83b-26: bdag gis rgyal ba bstod pa las //
T01TD1136E:83b-27: bsod nams bdag gis gang bsags pa //
T01TD1136E:83b-28: des ni sems can thams cad kyang //
T01TD1136E:83b-29: byang chub khong du chud par shog / phyag 'tshal ba'i bstod pa slob dpon 'phags pa klu sgrub kyis mdzad pa rdzogs so//
